# Clipboard fixture PAYLOADS are BYTE-EXACT test vectors: the paste specs
# compare round-tripped payloads against these files verbatim (CRLF row
# terminators, bare LF inside quoted TSV fields), so they must never be
# EOL-normalized. Scoped to the payload extensions only — README.md and
# generate-tellma.mts stay under the repo's normal EOL normalization policy.
*.txt -text
*.html -text
